      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他骂的莫非是花二娘？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这委实令人猜不透。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，不错……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风老四所骂的莫非就是此人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，这人看来果然像是个女子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "普天之下的女子，只有一人轻功如此了得，只怕就连",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qing_shu",
      "speaker_name": "铁青树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你老人家说的是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闪电卓三娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qing_shu",
      "speaker_name": "铁青树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱……咱们不如走吧，有这四人在这里……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，此时他们正自互相纠缠不清，咱们正可乘机脱身，若是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢再说走字！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qing_shu",
      "speaker_name": "铁青树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但不走又能……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "行动？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！司徒笑那恶贼却得留给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫正要瞧瞧彩虹七剑的身手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qing_shu",
      "speaker_name": "铁青树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你老人家的体力……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵是陈年老酒，也比不上仇人鲜血。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好孩子，不想你倒甚投老夫的脾胃。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我方才还骂了你老人家……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qing_shu",
      "speaker_name": "铁青树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕你方才是骂对了，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "否则怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qing_shu",
      "speaker_name": "铁青树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "否则只怕我便再也无法与你相见。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……那又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_qing_shu",
      "speaker_name": "铁青树",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没关系，我却是有关系的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我……我也有关系的……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ting",
      "speaker_name": "易挺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好恶贼，有你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "云老前辈手下留情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "孙小娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好妹子，原来是你，咱们险些大水冲了龙王庙……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "司……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，正是司徒笑。我和你哥哥一能走动，刚窜入草原，就遇着他们三个恶贼，他……他居然不顾旧情……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "易明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们来得正好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yi",
      "speaker_name": "云翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诱他们过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自是真的，你们在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "孙小娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里，你们还听不见么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，这次你们可千万莫要胡乱逃了，方才我说的话，只不过是向你们开开玩笑而已……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还是上当了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_xing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "黑星天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次看你们还往哪里逃？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
