      "speaker_name": "孙小娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你们要怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有什么，只不过要你们的命而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "孙小娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……这难道又是在开玩笑么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "孙小娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慢着！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "孙小娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彩虹七剑本是来帮你们的，你们为何……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "孙小娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但你难道不顾我和你那一段……",
